    "description": "<p>Effect: Connection – Teatime. If the user is in their Phony Forme, the user has +15% EHR and RES and their Special- and Status-Category Attacks targeting other creatures have a 20% chance of giving their target @Affliction[delay 20].</p><p>If the user is a Antique Forme, the user and their allies heal 30% more HP from @Trait[healing] Actions, and they gain 3 PP and @Affliction[advance 10] when consuming @Trait[food] items.</p><p>The user gains Cursed Body as an Extra Ability.</p>"
